    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not that people don't care, it's just that caring is part of the weight. i'm so tired of trying to \"feel better\" or \"find hope\" when the very thing that made life worth living is gone. everything just feels broken. i just want the heaviness to stop. i just want to finally be at peace and not have to struggle through another day of this emptiness.",
